k|2006|p=215}}\n| style=\"border-left: 3px solid grey;\" | 21\n| 13 July 1942\n| 09:58\n| [[Kharkiv KhAI-5|R-10]]{{sfn|Prien|Stemmer|Rodeike|Bock|2006|p=217}}\n|\n|-\n| 11\n| 24 June 1942\n| 18:17\n| Yak-4\n| northeast of Stary Tschenoissinowo{{sfn|Prien|Stemmer|Rodeike|Bock|2006|p=215}}\n| style=\"border-left: 3px solid grey;\" | 22\n| 26 July 1942\n| 16:15\n| LaGG-3{{sfn|Prien|Stemmer|Rodeike|Bock|2006|p=219}}\n|\n|-\n| 12\n| 2 July 1942\n| 07:00\n| MiG-3{{sfn|Prien|Stemmer|Rodeike|Bock|2006|p=216}}\n|\n| style=\"border-left: 3px solid grey;\" | 23\n| 26 July 1942\n| 16:18\n| LaGG-3{{sfn|Prien|Stemmer|Rodeike|Bock|2006|p=219}}\n|\n|-\n| 13\n| 2 July 1942\n| 12:10\n| [[Douglas A-20 Havoc|Boston]]{{sfn|Prien|Stemmer|Rodeike|Bock|2006|p=216}}\n|\n| style=\"border-left: 3px solid grey;\" | 24\n| 28 July 1942\n| 13:13\n| LaGG-3{{sfn|Prien|Stemmer|Rodeike|Bock|2006|p=219}}\n|\n|-\n| 14\n| 2 July 1942\n| 12:13\n| Boston{{sfn|Prien|Stemmer|Rodeike|Bock|2006|p=216}}\n|\n| style=\"border-left: 3px solid grey;\" | 25\n| 31 July 1942\n| 11:05\n| Pe-2\n| southeast of [[Kalach-na-Donu|Kalach]]{{sfn|Prien|Stemmer|Rodeike|Bock|2006|p=219}}\n|-\n| 15\n| 3 July 1942\n| 19:25\n| Il-2{{sfn|Prien|Stemmer|Rodeike|Bock|2006|p=216}}\n|\n| style=\"border-left: 3px solid grey;\" | 26\n| 31 July 1942\n| 11:42\n| Il-2\n| west of Kletskaja{{sfn|Prien|Stemmer|Rodeike|Bock|2006|p=219}}\n|-\n| 16\n| 3 July 1942\n| 19:26\n| Il-2{{sfn|Prien|Stemmer|Rodeike|Bock|2006|p=216}}\n|\n| style=\"border-left: 3px solid grey;\" | 27\n| 7 August 1942\n| 17:40\n| Pe-2\n| southwest of [[Stalingrad]]{{sfn|Prien|Stemmer|Rodeike|Bock|2006|p=220}}\n|-\n| 17\n| 4 July 1942\n| 17:16\n| Boston{{sfn|Prien|Stemmer|Rodeike|Bock|2006|p=216}}\n|\n| style=\"border-left: 3px solid grey;\" | 28\n| 7 August 1942\n| 17:41\n| Pe-2\n| {{Convert|40|km|mi|abbr=on}} southwest of Stalingrad{{sfn|Prien|Stemmer|Rodeike|Bock|2006|p=220}}\n|-\n| 18\n| 4 July 1942\n| 17:17\n| Boston{{sfn|Prien|Stemmer|Rodeike|Bock|2006|p=216}}\n|\n| styl