32}}\n|-\n| 63\n| 9 May 1943\n| 06:55\n| LaGG-3\n| Bataysk{{sfn|Prien|Stemmer|Rodeike|Bock|2012|p=129}}\n| style=\"border-left: 3px solid grey;\" | 86\n| 11 July 1943\n| 13:35\n| La-5\n| PQ 35 Ost 6124, southeast of Werchopenje{{sfn|Prien|Stemmer|Rodeike|Bock|2012|p=133}}\n|-\n| 64\n| 9 May 1943\n| 16:10\n| Pe-2\n| northeast of Krasnyi Lyman{{sfn|Prien|Stemmer|Rodeike|Bock|2012|p=129}}\n| style=\"border-left: 3px solid grey;\" | 87\n| 11 July 1943\n| 13:35\n| La-5\n| PQ 35 Ost 6124, southeast of Werchopenje{{sfn|Prien|Stemmer|Rodeike|Bock|2012|p=133}}\n|-\n| 65\n| 12 May 1943\n| 05:05\n| Il-2\n| southwest of [[Izium]]{{sfn|Prien|Stemmer|Rodeike|Bock|2012|p=129}}\n| style=\"border-left: 3px solid grey;\" | 88\n| 13 July 1943\n| 05:39\n| La-5\n| PQ 35 Ost 6287, west of Prokhorovka{{sfn|Prien|Stemmer|Rodeike|Bock|2012|p=133}}\n|-\n| 66\n| 14 May 1943\n| 17:35\n| Il-2\n| east of Pribodnoje{{sfn|Prien|Stemmer|Rodeike|Bock|2012|p=129}}\n| style=\"border-left: 3px solid grey;\" | 89\n| 13 July 1943\n| 05:41\n| La-5\n| PQ 35 Ost 6288, west of Prokhorovka{{sfn|Prien|Stemmer|Rodeike|Bock|2012|p=133}}\n|-\n| 67\n| 24 May 1943\n| 07:14\n| I-16\n| west of Bataysk{{sfn|Prien|Stemmer|Rodeike|Bock|2012|p=129}}\n| style=\"border-left: 3px solid grey;\" | 90\n| 15 July 1943\n| 18:10\n| Pe-2\n| PQ 35 Ost 7072, Izium{{sfn|Prien|Stemmer|Rodeike|Bock|2012|p=133}}\n|-\n| 68\n| 24 May 1943\n| 07:17\n| I-16\n| west of Bataysk{{sfn|Prien|Stemmer|Rodeike|Bock|2012|p=129}}\n| style=\"border-left: 3px solid grey;\" | 91\n| 16 July 1943\n| 04:57\n| La-5\n| east of Izium{{sfn|Prien|Stemmer|Rodeike|Bock|2012|p=133}}\n|-\n| 69\n| 10 June 1943\n| 08:45\n| La-5\n| north of Starobjelsk-Ost{{sfn|Prien|Stemmer|Rodeike|Bock|2012|p=130}}\n| style=\"border-left: 3px solid grey;\" | 92\n| 16 July 1943\n| 18:25\n| Yak-1\n| PQ 34 Ost 89142{{sfn|Prien|Stemmer|Rodeike|Bock|2012|p=133}}\n|-\n| 70\n| 11 June 1943\n| 11:01\n| La-5\n| east of Pokrowskoje{{sfn|Prien|Stemmer|Rodeike|Bock|2012|p=130}}\n| style=\"borde