 Foreman.{{sfn|Matthews|Foreman|2014|pp=501\u2013502}}|group=\"Note\"|name=\"not listed\"}}{{refn|This claim is also not listed by Prien, Stemmer, Rodeike and Bock.{{sfn|Prien|Stemmer|Rodeike|Bock|2008|p=329}}|group=\"Note\"}}\n| 1 October 1943\n| 13:44\n| [[Boeing B-17 Flying Fortress|B-17]]{{sfn|Prien|Stemmer|1996|p=501}}\n|\n| style=\"border-left: 3px solid grey;\" | 107\n| 19 December 1943\n| 12:28\n| B-17{{sfn|Prien|Stemmer|1996|p=501}}\n| PQ 04 Ost S/KC{{sfn|Prien|Stemmer|Rodeike|Bock|2008|p=329}}\n|-\n| style=\"background:#faecc8\" | 105?<ref group=\"Note\" name=\"not listed\"/>\n| 14 October 1943\n| 14:45\n| B-17{{sfn|Prien|Stemmer|1996|p=501}}\n| southeast of [[Schweinfurt]]{{sfn|Prien|Stemmer|Rodeike|Bock|2008|p=329}}\n| style=\"border-left: 3px solid grey; background:#faecc8\" | 108?<ref group=\"Note\" name=\"not listed\"/>\n| 23 February 1944\n| {{Center|\u2014}}\n| [[Consolidated B-24 Liberator|B-24]]{{sfn|Prien|Stemmer|1996|p=502}}\n|\n|-\n| style=\"background:#faecc8\" | 106?<ref group=\"Note\" name=\"not listed\"/>{{refn|This claim is also not listed by Prien and Stemmer.{{sfn|Prien|Stemmer|1996|p=501}}|group=\"Note\"}}\n| 14 October 1943\n| 14:55\n| style=\"background:#C0EFBA\" | B-17*\n| north of [[Arnstein]]{{sfn|Prien|Stemmer|Rodeike|Bock|2008|p=329}}\n| style=\"border-left: 3px solid grey;\" |\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|}\n\n===Awards===\n* [[Iron Cross]] (1939) 2nd and 1st Class\n* [[Honor Goblet of the Luftwaffe]] on 31 August 1942 as ''[[Leutnant]]'' and pilot{{sfn|Patzwall|2008|p=52}}\n* [[German Cross]] in Gold on 19 October 1942 as a ''Leutnant'' in the I./''Jagdgeschwader'' 3{{sfn|Patzwall|Scherzer|2001|p=44}}\n* [[Knight's Cross of the Iron Cross]] on 29 August 1943 as an ''[[Oberleutnant]]'' (war officer) and ''[[Staffelkapit\u00e4n]]'' of the 8./''Jagdgeschwader'' 3 \"Udet\"{{sfn|Scherzer|2007|p=223}}{{sfn|Fellgiebel|2000|p=134}}\n\n==Notes==\n{{Reflist|group=\"Note\"}}\n\n==References==\n\n===Citations===\n{{Reflist|25em}}\n\n===Bibliography===\n{